ng in autonomous\nvehicles, to suggest an optimal speed in human-driven vehicles and to improve\nthe comfort for bus-line services or even trains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2020 13:32:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-13"}
